pachmarhi madhya pradesh india in  he pursued his secondary education at the prestigious bangalore military school thereafter he joined the indian institute of technology kharagpur and graduated with a btech degree in metallurgical engineering in  in  he gained a ms in engineering and an mba from the haas school of business at the university of california berkeley careeredit early career and airtouch   edit he started his career as a management consultant before moving in  to pacific telesis group in san francisco he was a director of airtouch from july  and was president and chief operating officer from february  he was responsible for the worldwide operations and strategy of the mobile phone companycitation needed vodafone   edit airtouch was sold to vodafone in  for about  billion he was then appointed vodafones chief executive officer for the united states and asia pacific region until  april  when vodafones us interests were merged into verizon wireless he subsequently became chief executive of infospace in  and of accelkkr telecom based in san francisco from  to  while serving as a nonexecutive director of vodafone he rejoined vodafone as chief executive designate on  april  and was appointed on a permanent basis after the companys annual general meeting on  july  on  may  he announced his resignation effective july as ceo after vodafone achieved record earningscitation needed during his tenure as chief executive of vodafone group plc he expanded the company geographically into countries like india turkey south africa etc increasing the customer base to approximately  million he expanded the product line of the company to include data internet and broadband services he streamlined the operations of the company under the vodafone brand to utilize the global scale while maintaining local customer focus he increased the dividends per share by  percent and returned value to shareholders through buybackscitation needed sarin retired from vodafone immediately after the companys annual general meeting on july   and was succeeded by then deputyceo vittorio colao colao is paid a  pounds salary compared with the  million pounds sarin received at the end of march  according to the groups annual report and accounts published after vodafone   till dateedit in october  sarin was appointed as a senior advisor at the private equity firm kohlberg kravis roberts  co kkr he is a strategic advisor to the indianbased music streaming service saavn and owns a minority stake in the company boardedit he serves on the board of directors of ola cabs cisco systems accenture and charles schwab he also sits on the board of trustees for the blum center for developing economies at the university of california berkeley referencesedit  arun sarin conferred honorary knighthood retrieved    arun sarin  alumni profiles fulltime mba program  haas school of business uc berkeley mbahaasberkeleyedu retrieved    vodafone announces new chief executive vodafone  retrieved    vodafone cambio al vertice sarin si dimette è lora di colao corriere della sera in italian milan    arun sarin walks out of vodafone rich the times of india press trust of india pti    kkr  kkr appoints arun sarin as senior advisor mediakkrcom retrieved    saavn reaches  million monthly users adds exvodafone ceo as investoradvisor billboard retrieved    exvodafone global ceo arun sarin joins ola board the hindu   accenture announces appointment of arun sarin to its board of directors accenture   board blum center for developing economies  retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlearunsarinoldid categories  birthsliving peopleindian emigrants to the united statesamerican technology chief executivesamerican businessmen of indian descentuniversity of california berkeley college of engineering alumnivodafone peopleindian institute of technology kharagpur alumniamerican people of indian punjabi descenthaas school of business alumnipeople from pachmarhihidden categories cs italianlanguage sour