d expanded its services to include data and broadband following his retirement in  he served as a senior advisor to kohlberg kravis roberts  co for five years mr sarin is a director of blackhawk network holdings charles schwab corporation and cisco systems he previously served as a director of the gap and safeway and as a nonexecutive director of the court of the bank of england in  he was named an honorary knight of the british empire for services to the communications industry mr sarin holds mba and master of science engineering degrees from university of californiaberkeley and earned his bachelor of science degree from the indian institute of technology in kharagpur india compensation committee member nominating  governance committee member localnbsp toll freenbsp contact usnbspnbsp find a locationnbspnbsp about accenturenbspnbsp privacy policynbspnbsp cookie policynbspnbsp terms of usenbspnbsp site mapnbspnbsp accessibility statementnbspnbsp careersnbspnbsp by using this site you agree that we can place cookies on your device see our privacy policy and cookie policy for details nbsp accenture all rights reserved contact us find a location localnbsp toll freenbsp about accenture privacy policy cookie policy terms of use site map accessibility statement careers by using this site you agree that we can place cookies on your device see our privacy policy and cookie policy for details nbsp accenture all rights reserved select your location no results found we were unable to find a match for searchstring try searching again by using different or more general keywords and check for spelling errors recommended content filter results filter results connect with our talent community personalize your accenture career search and receive tailored news insights and job alerts join our talent connection to learn more about the challenging and rewarding career opportunities offered by accenture register already applied to a job if you have applied for a position in a location o